---
title: Garlic Chilli Prawn & Risoni Salad  with Yoghurt Dressing & Almonds
description: A fresh and filling salad is just what the doctor ordered - loads of crunchy veg, risoni for a source of satisfying carbs, yoghurt and nuts for healthy fats and lots of texture, and lean protein in the form of pan-fried prawns. This one ticks all the boxes!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
